OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPartly
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening with some late
OL,7,Fhazy sunshine. The rest of the night
OL,8,Fwill be predominately dry with clear
OL,9,Fspells, but the odd shower possible in
OL,10,Fthe west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA mainly dry and bright
OL,13,Fstart. Showery outbreaks of rain will
OL,14,Fthen develop during the morning and
OL,15,Fmove east through the afternoon.
OL,16,FRather breezy around coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
